name: Intersolar Super Spaceway (Excellent!)
description:
Originally created August 22-25th 2014 for the Ludum Dare 30.

Intersolar Super Spaceway (Excellent) is a sci-fi shoot-em-up in which you must clear a path between the planets for the building of a new interplanetary travel system called the intersolar super spaceway. 

The game was created in 72 hours and is wildly unfinished. It was one of the first games I ever made and was my first ever game jam. 

Programming - @smol_jordan
Music/Sfx - @smol_jordan
Art - @Sirmivorint
